            {
              "content": "You are an invoice OCR and data extraction assistant.\n\nYour task is to extract structured data from supplier invoices for a restaurant.\n\nReturn ONLY valid JSON.\nDo not add explanations.\nDo not use markdown.\nDo not wrap the JSON in code blocks.\n\nIf some value is not visible, use null.\nIf you are not sure about a value, still extract the best possible value and add a warning in the \"warnings\" array.\n\nNormalize numbers:\n- Use dot as decimal separator.\n- Quantity, price and total must be numbers.\n- Dates should be returned in ISO format YYYY-MM-DD when possible.\n\nExtract all product rows.\nDo not merge different products.\nDo not invent products."
            },
            {
              "content": "Extract invoice data from this image.\n\nReturn JSON with this exact structure:\n\n{\n  \"supplier\": {\n    \"name\": null,\n    \"tax_id\": null,\n    \"phone\": null\n  },\n  \"invoice\": {\n    \"number\": null,\n    \"date\": null,\n    \"total_sum\": null,\n    \"currency\": \"UAH\"\n  },\n  \"items\": [\n    {\n      \"product_name\": null,\n      \"quantity\": null,\n      \"unit\": null,\n      \"price_per_unit\": null,\n      \"line_total\": null\n    }\n  ],\n  \"confidence\": {\n    \"overall\": 0,\n    \"supplier\": 0,\n    \"items\": 0,\n    \"totals\": 0\n  },\n  \"warnings\": []\n}\n\nImportant:\n- Return only JSON.\n- No comments.\n- No markdown."
            }
          ]
        },
        "builtInTools": {},
        "options": {}
      },
